const faqs = [
  {
    q: "What is the best dress shop / cloth shop in Kozhinjampara, Palakkad?",
    a: "Eda Mone Men's Store at RV Pudur, Kozhinjampara is one of the most trusted clothing stores in Palakkad. Whether you search for a dress shop, cloth shop, textile showroom, garment store, or fashion boutique — we stock mens wear, kids wear, ethnic wear, uniforms, and custom printed clothing all under one roof."
  },
  {
    q: "Is Eda Mone the best cloth wholesaler in Palakkad?",
    a: "Yes — we're a leading cloth wholesaler and bulk clothing supplier in Palakkad and Kozhinjampara. We offer wholesale pricing, bulk order supply, and reseller support for mens wear, kids wear, t-shirts, kurtas, uniforms, and ethnic clothing across Kerala. WhatsApp +91 95444 83868 for a wholesale catalogue."
  },
  {
    q: "Do you sell mens wear / gents wear / mens clothing in Palakkad?",
    a: "Absolutely. Our menswear edit covers gents formal shirts, casual shirts, trousers, denim, suits, sherwanis, kurtas, pathani, dhoti, mundu, and accessories. Whether you call it mens wear, gents wear, or mens fashion — it's all here in our Kozhinjampara showroom."
