    a: "Yes — we supply bulk orders and wholesale clothing to shops, resellers, event organizers, schools, offices, and teams across Kerala. Bulk pricing is available for t-shirts, shirts, kurtas, uniforms, and printed apparel. Contact us on WhatsApp for a quote."
